Gesture Dino Game

## ğŸ¯ Overview

This project is a **Chrome Dinoâ€“style running game** controlled entirely by **hand gestures** â€” no keyboard or mouse needed!

You jump using your **open palm**, detected in real time via your webcam using **MediaPipe** and **OpenCV**.  
The game visuals and physics are built using **Pygame**.


## ğŸ§© Main Features

- âœ… Hand Gesture Jump (Open Palm â†’ Jump)  
- âœ… Auto-detect ground level from background image  
- âœ… Increasing speed and score as game progresses  
- âœ… Smooth restart after collision  
- âœ… Real-time webcam window showing gesture detection  
- âœ… Fully offline â€” runs locally with camera  


